import axios from 'axios'; import React, { useContext, useEffect, useState } from 'react' import { useParams } from 'react-router-dom'; import flightContent from "../context/FlightContext"; import '../styles/FetchBooking.css' import Button from '../components/Button' const FetchBooking = () => { const content = useContext(flightContent) const { createPdf, getPdf } = content const [fetchbooking, setFetchBooking] = useState([]) const [fetchpassenger, setFetchPassenger] = useState([]) const viewBooking = async (bid) => { const { data } = await axios.get(`/auth/myflight?_id=${bid}`) const fdata = data if (fdata.success) { setFetchBooking(fdata.flights) const { data } = await axios.get(`auth/getpassofbook?_id=${bid}`) const pdata = data if (pdata.success) { setFetchPassenger(pdata.passenger) } } } const params = useParams() useEffect(() => { viewBooking(params.slug) }, []) const download = async (bid) => { const { data } = await axios(`/myflight?_id=${bid}`); const pbdata = data if (pbdata.success) { const { data } = await axios(`/getpassofbook?_id=${bid}`) const bpdata = data console.log(bpdata) if (bpdata.success) { createPdf(bid, bpdata.passenger, pbdata.flights) .then(() => getPdf()) } } } return (
Booking Details
{fetchbooking.map((element) => { return <>
Outbound flight
{element.departuredate}
{element.flightname} {element.flightnumber}
DEPARTURE
{element.departurecode}-{element.departuretime}
{element.departuredate}
{element.departure}
{element.departureairport}
DURATION
3hr
ARRIVAL
{element.destinationcode}-{element.destinationtime}
{element.departuredate}
{element.destination}
{element.destinationairport}
{element.triptype === 'Return' ?
Outbound flight
{element.rdeparturedate}
{element.rflightname} {element.rflightnumber}
DEPARTURE
{element.rdeparturecode}-{element.rdeparturetime}
{element.rdeparturedate}
{element.rdeparture}
{element.rdepartureairport}
DURATION
3hr
ARRIVAL
{element.rdestinationcode}-{element.rdestinationtime}
{element.rdeparturedate}
{element.rdestination}
{element.rdestinationairport}
: <> }
Passenger Details
PASSENGER
TYPE
PHONE
EMAIL
{fetchpassenger.map((element) => { return <>
{element.firstname} {element.lastname}
Adult
{element.mobilenumber ? element.mobilenumber : '-'}
{element.email ? element.email : '-'}
}) }
Payment Details

} ) }
) } export default FetchBooking
